{
  "title": "SC-002C 废弃仓库 - 询问身份路线",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_001.png",
      "text": "旅人...这是我的代号？记忆清除？零号档案？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_001.png",
      "text": "那个人告诉我的事...代号旅人，潜入黄昏组织...记忆被故意清除的...",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_001.png",
      "text": "这里就是废弃仓库...那个接应者在哪里？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_002.png",
      "text": "你来了。我还以为你会问更多问题再离开。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_001.png",
      "text": "她知道那个人对我说了什么？她到底是谁？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_005.png",
      "text": "你一定有很多问题。关于旅人，关于零号档案...我知道的不多，但我知道你是谁。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_001.png",
      "text": "你到底是谁？你怎么知道这些？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_002.png",
      "text": "我叫林晓薇。我曾经是一名调查记者。在调查黄昏组织时，我遇到了你。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_004.png",
      "text": "那些追你的人，是黄昏组织的人。他们不想让你想起任何事。如果你恢复了记忆，对他们来说就是威胁。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "E:/workSpace/ai/task-art/lost-choices/assets/keyframes/ch1/sc_002_temp/frame_005.png",
      "text": "现在，你必须做出选择。相信我，让我帮你找回记忆。或者...我们可以交换信息。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    }
  ]
}
